 some good 1hs weapons that i can quest for or hunt for as a lvl 35 warrior.  I have been having the hardest time keeping aggro with my BABS when fighting yellow to red cons to me.  Any advice would be appreciated.<br>
<br>
Troll Warrior,<br>
<br>
Drez Swayy <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#1478A2><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub88.ezboard.com/bepicheroes73161.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=clarrissa>Clarrissa</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Officer</span><br>  Posts: 302<br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/15/01 10:05:54 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub88.ezboard.com/fepicheroes73161frm14.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=33.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Weapon Help</span><hr size=1> Short Sword of Yakesha <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#7c96b9><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub88.ezboard.com/uciynn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ciynn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 64<br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/15/01 10:16:29 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub88.ezboard.com/fepicheroes73161frm14.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=33.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Weapon Help</span><hr size=1> From my experience, 2HS really doesn’t go a very long way towards Taunt.  Sure, it delivers damage, but just doesn’t hit enough to keep that bad guy’s interest.  If you are main tank in your groups, low delay is a must.  In a secondary tank role the higher damage of a 2HS isn’t a bad option.  Clarrissa is right.  The SSOY is a great weapon for taunt.  I used to dual wield them before I got my Canes of Tranquil.  In fact, you may want to consider saving your coppers to get a couple of them.  I bought mine when they were still 1,100 – 1,500 a piece, but they are now in the 900 Platinum range—much like the SSOY.  However, you actually have a shot at being able to camp the SSOY at your level.<br>
<br>
<br>
Good Luck and let me know if I can help in any way!<br>
<br>
<br>
Ciynn Souljaded<br>
40th level Half-Elven Warrior<br>
